reviewText: In the unfortunate period of the present, where children are not taught about our historic legendary heroes, here is a story of one. Oh, it is not historically complete accurate, but it introduces them to the real people and those who were with here. A must for our young ones.
THIS IS A GREAT FAMILY MOVIE STARRING THE REKNOWNED JAMIE LEE CURTIS.IT'S A MUST SEE FOR ALL TO ENJOY THAT'S FINALLY ON DVD!!!!!
